#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &sheets; Configuration Dialog Box"
msgstr "&sheets; Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem> Configure "
"&sheets;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> opens a dialog box with several "
"pages, selected with the icons at the left of the dialog box, which allow "
"you to change many aspects of &sheets;'s operation."
msgstr ""
"Izbira <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem> Konfiguriraj "
"&sheets;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> odpre pogovorno okno z več stranmi, "
"izbranimi z ikonami na levi strani pogovornega okna, ki vam omogočajo "
"spreminjanje številnih vidikov delovanja &sheets;."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Vmesnik"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija vmesnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor movement after pressing Enter:"
msgstr "Premik kazalca po pritisku Enter:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select whether pressing the &Enter; key will move the cursor <guilabel>Down</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Up</guilabel>, <guilabel>Right</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Left</guilabel>, <guilabel>Down, First Column</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>None</guilabel> as determined by the setting in this drop down "
"selection box."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, ali s pritiskom tipke &Enter; tipka premakne kazalec "
"<guilabel>dol</guilabel>, <guilabel>gor</guilabel>, <guilabel>desno</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>levo</guilabel>, <guilabel>dol, prvi stolpec</guilabel> "
"ali <guilabel>Brez</guilabel>, kot določa nastavitev v tem spustnem izbirnem "
"polju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Function shown in the status bar:"
msgstr "Funkcija, prikazana v vrstici stanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This drop down selection box can be used to choose the calculation performed "
"by the <link linkend=\"statusbarsum\">Statusbar Summary </link> function."
msgstr ""
"To spustno izbirno polje lahko uporabite za izbiro izračuna, ki ga izvede "
"funkcija <link linkend=\"statusbarsum\">Povzetek vrstice stanja </link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unit:"
msgstr "Enota:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the default unit that will be used in your sheets."
msgstr "Izberite privzeto enoto, ki bo uporabljena v vaših listih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation step:"
msgstr "Korak zamika:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the amount of indent that will be used in the cell when you choose the "
"<guilabel>Increase Indent</guilabel>/<guilabel>Decrease Indent</guilabel> "
"actions from the toolbar. These actions are not enabled by default in the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite količino zamika, ki bo uporabljen v celici, ko v orodni vrstici "
"izberete dejanja <guilabel>Povečaj zamik</guilabel>/<guilabel>Zmanjšaj "
"zamik</guilabel>. Ta dejanja v orodni vrstici niso privzeto omogočena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capture all navigation keys while editing"
msgstr "Zajemite vse navigacijske tipke med urejanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Captures all navigation keys, &ie; the arrow keys, page up/down, tabulator "
"and backward tabulator key, while editing a cell with the embedded editor. "
"The embedded editor is the one appearing directly in the cell. If captured, "
"these keys are used for navigating in the editor. Otherwise, they are used "
"for cell navigation."
msgstr ""
"Zajame vse navigacijske tipke, &ie;. puščične tipke, stran gor/dol, "
"tabulator in tabulator nazaj, medtem ko urejate celico z vdelanim "
"urejevalnikom. Vdelani urejevalnik je tisti, ki se pojavi neposredno v "
"celici. Če so zajete, se te tipke uporabljajo za navigacijo v urejevalniku. "
"V nasprotnem primeru se uporabljajo za navigacijo celic."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Colors</guilabel> section lets you choose the color of the "
"sheet grid. If you do not want the grid to appear at all, uncheck the "
"<guilabel>Show grid</guilabel> box in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Sheet Properties</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Barve</guilabel> lahko izberete barvo mreže listov. Če "
"ne želite, da se mreža sploh prikaže, počistite polje <guilabel>Prikaži "
"mrežo</guilabel> v <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Lastnosti lista </guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section also lets you select the color of the lines used to indicate "
"the printed page borders when the <guimenuitem>Page Borders</guimenuitem> "
"box in the <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu is checked."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku lahko izberete tudi barvo črt, ki se uporabljajo za "
"označevanje obrob natisnjene strani, ko je označeno polje "
"<guimenuitem>Obrobe strani</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> from the current color to display the "
"standard &kde; <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Med trenutno barvo izberite <guilabel>Po meri</guilabel>, da prikažete "
"standardni &kde; Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi barvo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grid"
msgstr "Mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click here to change the grid color &ie; the color of the borders of each "
"cell."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite tukaj, če želite spremeniti barvo mreže &ie;. barvo obrob vsake "
"celice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page border"
msgstr "Obroba strani"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Page Borders</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item is checked, the page borders are "
"displayed. Click here to choose another color for the borders than the "
"default red."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označen menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži obrobe strani</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se "
"prikažejo obrobe strani. Kliknite tukaj, če želite izbrati drugo barvo obrob "
"poleg privzete rdeče."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save"
msgstr "Odpri/Shrani"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save Configuration."
msgstr "Odpri/Shrani konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of entries in Recent Files list:"
msgstr "Število vnosov na seznamu nedavnih datotek:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Controls the maximum number of filenames that are shown when you select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu> Open Recent</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Nadzoruje največje število imen datotek, ki so prikazana, ko izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu> Odpri nedavno</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autosave interval:"
msgstr "Interval samodejnega shranjevanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can select the time between autosaves, or disable this feature "
"altogether by choosing <guilabel>No autosave</guilabel> (by selecting the "
"minimum value)."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete čas med samodejnimi shranitvami ali popolnoma "
"onemogočite to funkcijo z izbiro <guilabel>Brez samodejnega shranjevanja</"
"guilabel> (z izbiro najmanjše vrednosti)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configdialog.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create backup file:"
msgstr "Ustvari varnostno kopijo datoteke:"

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want some backup files created. This is checked per "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite ustvariti nekaj varnostnih kopij datotek. To je "
"privzeto potrjeno."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija vtičnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check a plugin in the list to enable it. Display the <guilabel>About</"
"guilabel> dialog by clicking the info button at the right side of the list "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Preverite vtičnik na seznamu, da ga omogočite. Prikažite pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Vizitka</guilabel>, tako da kliknete gumb z informacijami na desni "
"strani elementa seznama."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spelling"
msgstr "Črkovanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spell Checker Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija črkovalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "This page lets you configure the behavior of &sheets;'s spell checker."
msgstr "Na tej strani lahko konfigurirate delovanje črkovalnika &sheets;."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information please refer to the <ulink url=\"help:kcontrol/"
"spellchecking\">Spell Checker</ulink> documentation."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte dokumentacijo o <ulink url=\"help:kcontrol/"
"spellchecking\">črkovalniku</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: configdialog.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author"
msgstr "Avtor"

#. Tag: phrase
#: configdialog.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Author Configuration."
msgstr "Konfiguracija avtorja."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose an author profile for your document."
msgstr "Izberite profil avtorja za svoj dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: configdialog.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a new profile or delete the current profile using the buttons to "
"the right of the profiles drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbi na desni strani spustnega seznama profilov lahko dodate nov profil "
"ali izbrišete trenutni profil."
